Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:49.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}爸爸.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:56.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}爸爸.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:00.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}利兰.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:03.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}爸爸.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:06.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}利兰.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:11.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}爸爸. 爸爸. 利兰.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy. Daddy. Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:13.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:16.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:20.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:23.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:27.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the right to an attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:30.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你有权请律师.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l waive that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我放弃这个权利.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm gonna ask you some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会问你一些问题.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything you say may be held\Nagainst you in a court of law.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:42.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的一切\N将会成为呈堂证供.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course, l do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:46.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,明白, 我当然明白.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On Friday morning, March 3rd,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:53.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,3月3日, 周五早晨,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did you go\Nto Calhoun Memorial Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:57.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有\N卡尔霍恩纪念医院?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:02:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:00.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去过.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:03.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你去那里干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:06.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我去探病.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who were you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,探谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who killed my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个杀了我女儿的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:17.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他的名字吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:19.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. l do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊. 我现在知道了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jacques Renault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:26.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雅克·雷诺.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What made you think\Nhe killed Laura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:31.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道是\N他杀了劳拉?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You arrested him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:34.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你逮捕了他.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did you kill Jacques Renault?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:48.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...是你杀了雅克·雷诺吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed my Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:54.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了我的劳拉.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:00.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们体验过这种
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,absolute loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:03.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对的痛失吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l doubt that any one of us\Nis a stranger to grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:07.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕我们之中\N都不曾有过如此的悲痛.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, more than grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:09.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 那不单只是悲痛.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's deep down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而是内心.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lnside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,最深处.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every cell screams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:19.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,每个细胞都在尖叫.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:22.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...再听不见别的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l ki--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:38.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:41.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:45.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 是, 是.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:05:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He'll plead temporary insanity.\N- We'll need a psychiatric exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:05:00.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 暂时先把他界定为精神失常.\N- 我们需要做个心理检查.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll tell you one thing,\Nparents should not bury their children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:03.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想告诉你,\N父母真不应该亲眼看着自己的孩子下葬.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who's been through\Nwhat Leland has is--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:05.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,换作是任何人\N像利兰这样--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you approve of murder,\NDr. Hayward?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:07.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那谋杀是对的囉,\N海沃德医生?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:15.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨, 医生.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How are you, Andy?\N- Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:19.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好吗, 安迪?\N- 还行.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:22.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很好. 好.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有问题?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's kind of personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:28.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,私人问题.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm your doctor, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的医生, 安迪.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's about my sperms test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:35.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是关于我的精子化验.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:37.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, l flunked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道, 我的精不行.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the precise term for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:42.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也没那么绝对.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l was just wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 我在想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if it's the kind of test\Nyou can take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:47.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是否可以\N帮我在做一次化验.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, like a driver's exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:50.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗, 像司机做的那种.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, l've been wearing boxer shorts\Nevery day just like you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:55.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说, 我已经按你说的\N每天只穿平脚裤.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna give it another shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你想再来一炮?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. l would.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:06:00.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 先生. 就这意思.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll need to take a sample with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我要带个样本回去.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right now?\N- Put it in a brown bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 马上?\N- 放在棕色的袋子里.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll wait in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在车上等你.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, l've got\Na garbage truck here on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:01.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}露西, 我这边\N有一台垃圾车正在...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:04.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 闭嘴.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our judge arrives this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:08.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们镇的法官下午回到.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clinton Sternwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:10.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,克林顿·斯登伍.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Travels the circuit in a Winnebago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,东部温尼贝戈地区他都走个遍了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outdoors enthusiast?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,越野爱好者?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last of the frontiersmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:16.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,终极拓荒者.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They broke the mold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这方土地都是他们开发的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l only got bail hearing for Leland\Nand Leo's competency examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:24.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而我只有利兰和里欧的\N保释听证会.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Leland get bail?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:25.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰可以保释吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Harry, that's up to\Nyour state prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 哈里, 那就要看\N你这儿的检察官了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be Daryl Lodwick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,检察官叫达里尔·罗威克.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也在来的路上了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When do we hear from Hawk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,豪克那边有消息吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He called this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他今早打过电话来.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the county...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 县里...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:41.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...说没有一个\N叫罗伯逊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...says nobody\Nby the name of Robertson
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:44.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在帕尔默家\N旁边住过.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had ever lived\Nnext to the Palmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:48.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们拿到最后一个房客\N的现住址了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a current address\Non the last occupants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在蒙大拿州的卡列斯佩尔.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalispell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,下午前派人过去查.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll check it by afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:56.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿. 看着点, 安迪.\N- 对不起, 鲍勃.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey. Watch it, Andy.\N- Sorry, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:58.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 我的天啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:07.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪, 别动.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:11.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在哪里搞到这个的?\N- 别逼我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where did you get those?\N- Don't make me say
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:13.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,到底从哪儿来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where these came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:15.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:21.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别问了, 库珀探员,\N这个绝对是个人隐私.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Agent Cooper,\Nthis is extremely personal business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:23.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的靴子?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your boots?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:26.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 不好意思.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:31.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天菲利普·杰勒德在等你们时\N我帮他买的. 真抱歉.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l bought these from Phillip Gerard\Nyesterday when he was waiting. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:37.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和里欧的那双\N是一个牌子.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the same brand of boots\Nwe found at Leo Johnson's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,巨人说\N线索会在这里出现.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Giant said\Nthere was a clue out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是可卡因呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought it was the cocaine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:45.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 一定要找到菲利普·杰勒德,\N独臂人.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, we've gotta find Phillip Gerard,\Nthe one-armed man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以走了吗, 库珀探员?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can l go now, Agent Cooper?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我赶时间.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know how much time l've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:51.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你赶,先走吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 露西怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:08:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, what's with Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:20.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 荷恩先生.\N- 边走边说.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Horne.\N- Walk and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:22.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我一个在西雅图派邮件\N的朋友.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This friend of mine works\Nwith the Seattle Post-Dispatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:26.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,其实, 她是我妹的大学校友\N但也算是我的朋友了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, my sister went to college\Nwith her but she's a friend of mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:30.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,反正, 她今早打电话来报了个\N猛料. 最高机密.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, she called me this morning\Nwith a hot tip. Top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:33.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安·提·文思要来\N双峰镇了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M.T. Wentz is coming\Nto Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:35.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安·提·文思, 安·提·文思.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M.T. Wentz. M.T. Wentz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:38.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安·提·文思, 那个游记作家.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M.T. Wentz, the travel writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对, 安·提·文思, 游记作家.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, M.T. Wentz the travel writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:44.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,文思出行从来不用真名,\N和信用卡, 只付现金.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wentz travels incognito,\Nuses only cash, no credit cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以没有人知道他到底是谁.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can trace his identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:50.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是女的. 报纸上也从没说\N这人是男是女.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or hers. No one at the paper\Neven knows who he or she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:53.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有价值,文思的到访\N或许有利我们酒店宣传.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Favorable Wentz review\Ncould be quite useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:55.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是, 他快来了.\N快要来了, 快要来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's coming.\NHe's coming, he's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:58.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我在前台盯着.\N每小时更新一次信息.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep an eye on the registration.\Nl want an hourly update.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:10:01.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 仔细核对每一张单据.\N- 特别是付现金的.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Scrutinize every check.\N- Especially if they pay cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:07.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还没到9:30下班\N你就已经做好了一天的工作了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even 9:30 and you have\Nalready done a good day's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:20.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,荷恩先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Horne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你气色不错啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:27.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有什么可以帮你吗?\N- 哦, 我们见过.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What can l do for you?\N- Oh, we've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我推销小企业\N保险业务.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l sell insurance\Nto the small business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,像独眼杰克赌场.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like One-Eyed Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尚·雷诺.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean Renault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有何贵干?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的保险费\N又涨价了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are my premiums\Nabout to be raised?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:44.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 不. 不是那样的.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:46.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请坐.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:48.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请坐.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:11.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个浑蛋.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:16.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你这个浑蛋!\N- 先别误会, 荷恩先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You bastard!\N- Make no mistake, Mr. Horne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来传话的.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm just the messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:19.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,帮谁传?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:25.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要一大笔赎金.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They request a large sum of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:28.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:32.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有其他要求.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l require something else entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们应该承担\N中介费.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should bear the cost\Nof their own middleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:39.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,第一.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你那里的生意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your business up there
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:44.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,已经慢慢给那些\N吃里扒外的庸才侵蚀.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is being run\Nby pickpockets and fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:46.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,赚到的钱左手进右手出.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dollar earned is a dollar stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:49.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你注意到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aware of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:50.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就怀疑了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have my suspicions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:53.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要一个合伙人.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you need is a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:57.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个可以帮你\N处理这些琐事的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who can take care\Nof these little problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:12:00.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我已经有合伙人了.\N- 那好.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l have a partner.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:03.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那你到底想不想我帮你?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want my help or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:09.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,想.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:12.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:19.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要这个人\N带赎金过来.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want this man\Nto bring to me the ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:22.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是联邦调查局的探员.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is an FBl agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:25.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你想赎回你女儿吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want your daughter back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:28.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这当然, 我当然想赎回女儿\N但我不能--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, l want my daughter back\Nbut l can't--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:31.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现金...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cash...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...合伙人...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:37.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...探员.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...FBl man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:40.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个交易\N还真划算.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is supposed to be\Nan equitable exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,顺其自然就好.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could turn out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:51.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那明天等你电话...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Expect a call tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:53.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...中午.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:16.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮特.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Janet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,快给我找库珀探员.\N急事.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find Agent Cooper for me.\Nlt's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:26.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你开玩笑吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:28.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他长得怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哇, 唐娜,\N你今天好漂亮.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're looking\Nreal pretty today, Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢.\N- 约会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thanks.\N- Special occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:36.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对. 送餐时认识的\N约了他一起吃午饭.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. l'm having lunch today\Nwith someone l met on my route.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:40.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,老尿壶和自闭症.\N有什么好约会的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bedpans and shut-ins.\NWho's to meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会理解的.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:46.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别把汤洒了.\N- 谢了, 路易.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't spill the soup.\N- Thanks, Louie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 有好消息.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,北方酒店的那个路易\N刚给我打了电话.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just got a call from Louie\Nat the Northern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:53.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安·提·文思\N要来双峰镇了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M.T. Wentz is coming\Nto Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:55.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,菩提·肉丝是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Empty who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:58.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,汉克, 他是我国最有威望的\N一个美食评论家.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hank, he's the most powerful\Nrestaurant critic in the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的?\N- 是啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:13:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Really?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他能在西雅图邮报\N上为我们美言几句
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a good review\Nfrom him and his Seattle paper
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:03.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们双食店就火了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,could give us a lot of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:06.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,路易说会想办法\N介绍他过来吃饭.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's gonna try to\Nsend him our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:10.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他长什么样子?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:13.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个, 每人见过.\N我猜是个秘密.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, nobody knows.\Nl guess it's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但估计他\N今天就会到.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's supposed to be\Narriving today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:18.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们还有时间.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we still got time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:21.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么时间, 汉克?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for what, Hank?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:27.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么时间, 汉克?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for what, Hank?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:32.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去采些花回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm gonna pick up some flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有漂亮的蜡烛\N和桌布.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and maybe some candles\Nand some tablecloths.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:39.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,菜牌上你看再加点什么菜式?\N特别点的.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what can we add to the menu?\NSome specials maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:41.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想\N加些地方小菜了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l always wanted to try\Nsome regional dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:46.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝, 我们要把这里打扮得漂漂亮亮\N就像过圣诞和国庆一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Babe, we're gonna trick this place out\Nlike Christmas on the Fourth of July.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:49.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 我觉得\N你应该打个电话给大个儿艾德.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and l think\Nyou should give Big Ed a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么?\N- 嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why?\N- Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...你们不是好朋友吗, 对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're still friendly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个文思可能\N会停在那儿加油.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe this Wentz guy\Nstops in for gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:15:00.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要是艾德见到陌生人\N叫他通知一声.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ed could suggest the Double R\Nto any new faces he sees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:03.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我会跟他说的.\N- 好.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l'll call him.\N- Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:05.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,记住了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:23.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:26.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...为什么干杯好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what shall we drink to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:28.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为劳拉.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:32.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为劳拉.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:35.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,铭刻心中.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln our hearts and memories, locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:49.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她的日记.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:52.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉过你她日记的事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did l tell you l had it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:54.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉的日记?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura's diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你读一段怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall l read something from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今天似乎很合适.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt seems appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:02.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,读吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:17.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"但我还是不敢告诉她\N我的美梦和恶梦.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''But still l'm afraid to tell her\Nof my fantasies and my nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:19.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有时她会\N理解我说的.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes she's good\Nat understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但大多数时候她都会笑话我\N而我也没有这个勇气告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other times she just giggles\Nand l don't have the nerve to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂她听了\N有什么会觉得好笑.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why things like that\Nare funny to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:31.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我却感觉遭透了\N所以我很长一段时间没再提起.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So l feel badly again\Nand shut up about it for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是那么的爱唐娜--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l love Donna very mu--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:38.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但有时我又很害怕\N她再也不在我身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes l worry that\Nshe wouldn't be around me at all
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:42.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她知道我内心的\N困扰吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if she knew what my insides\Nwere like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:47.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,暗黑的力量\N渗透了我的梦...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and dark\Nand soaked with dreams of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:52.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...那,那高个儿男人也许会\N想方设法捉到我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...big, big men and different ways\Nthat they might hold me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:55.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和控制我."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take me into their control.''
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:00.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:02.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别, 别这样说.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:05.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯-- 我只是觉得, 我是说--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l-- l was just, l mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:09.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说, 这也算是证据,\N我们不是应该交给警方吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, if that's evidence,\Nshouldn't we give that to the sheriff?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:12.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我意思是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:18.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我-- 我已经\N从头到尾看过了, 唐娜,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've-- l've read this\Nfrom cover to cover, Donna,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:21.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里面没有答案.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there are no solutions here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:26.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...是她给我的东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:28.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:34.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,人们来我这里\N讲他们的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People come to me\Nand tell me their stories
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:37.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在外面的故事.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about the world outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:42.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我聆听\N并用文字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l take their stories\Nand place them
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:45.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,记录下来.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a larger context.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再整理成小说.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sort of living novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:49.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谁和你讲故事?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who tells you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 朋友.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:55.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爱人.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:02.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 或许, 某天, 你也愿意讲.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe, someday, you will too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:12.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,给你说中了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:15.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那些绑匪今天上午\N联系我了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her kidnappers contacted me\Nthis morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:18.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真该死, 而你是对的.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn me, but you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不报警?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you alert the sheriff?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:25.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果警方介入,他们会立刻杀了她\N所以我才找你来.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll kill her at first sign of police\Ninvolvement. That's why l called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:27.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但这不是理由来规避\N正常的办案渠道.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no reason to circumvent\Nnormal channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:32.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,按常规办案\N我女儿就没法活着回来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal channels won't bring\Nmy daughter back to me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:37.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你和欧蕊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Audrey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,关系特别.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a special relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:45.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你, 所有人,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, of all people,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:48.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,都知道她对我多重要.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,understand her value to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:53.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们明天\N就要赎金.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They wanna make\Nthe exchange tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:59.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...12万5千美金.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for $1 25,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:01.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现金.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:05.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我请求你.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l must ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:11.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能送钱过去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you take it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:22.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:25.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 皮特.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Pete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真难过.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:31.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 我也是.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:34.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道, 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:37.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...老是想起安德鲁.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...keep thinking about Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:40.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他在会怎样处理\N这次火灾.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What he would have done\Nabout the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:44.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢天谢地还有凯瑟琳\N在这里处理.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness Catherine was here\Nto handle everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:52.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:56.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳烧死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine died in the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:58.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝, 不会的.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:01.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 皮特.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Pete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:04.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 皮特.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Pete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:11.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:14.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要准备葬礼了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're planning a service...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:18.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...但他们还没找到尸体.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they haven't found the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:20.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 皮特.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Pete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:23.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,过两天就要举行了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln a couple of days we'll go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:29.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还真不知道\N到时候葬什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know exactly\Nwhat we'll be burying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:42.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这边. 过来,\N游魂鬼. 爸爸来接你了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right this way. Come on,\Ndreamboat. Daddy's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:45.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,快来.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:50.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,荷恩小姐真不乖,\N什么要都不吃.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Horne was a very bad girl,\Nrefusing to take her medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:53.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 请别.\N- 没错吧, 荷恩小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Please.\N- Weren't you, Miss Horne?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:55.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:58.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:01.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有人虐待你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have you been mistreated?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:06.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他打我.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.31,0:21:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:10.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我没打她.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l did not hit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:13.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别听她说, 我没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf that's what you're thinking, l didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:15.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不对了.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:20.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你和我在一起\N就再也不会发生了.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt will never happen again\Nas long as you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:22.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:27.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我今早和你爸爸\N谈过了.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l spoke with your father\Nthis morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:30.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会有危险的.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in no danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:34.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,事情进行得很顺利.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:36.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:37.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你会的, 欧蕊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you, Audrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.59,0:21:40.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看, 欧蕊,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, Audrey,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.97,0:21:43.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在这情形,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a situation like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:47.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你要管好自己\N友善点.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to handle yourself\Nin a professional manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:51.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是明白人\N至于你知道的那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all reasonable people\Nand what you discover
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:55.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,明白人做明白事\N我们可以坐下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that something reasonable\Ncan always be worked out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:58.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢谈\N我们会理解的--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whenever reasonable people\Njust put their minds--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:10.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别哭.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.65,0:22:38.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,露西?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.94,0:22:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.98,0:22:41.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,露西, 我们要谈谈.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.27,0:22:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, we need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:45.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,布伦南副警长,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Brennan,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.82,0:22:49.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你更应该\N和你的色情杂志谈去?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.11,0:22:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought you preferred\Nthe company of your magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:54.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:56.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是先出去透透气吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you'd better get some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:04.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,露西,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:07.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么困扰着你\N不如说出来我听听
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.56,0:23:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think we're at the point where\Nit would be healthier for everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:11.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,找出问题, 这样\N对大家都有好处.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you got whatever was\Nbothering you out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:17.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪和我以前谈过恋爱.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy and l used to go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.69,0:23:19.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个我知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.98,0:23:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That much l gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.11,0:23:24.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一起有一年半了,我开始发觉他\N有点不对劲.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a year and a half until l started\Nto notice things about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.95,0:23:29.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是什么大事,\N就是些小毛病.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.22,0:23:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't big things,\Nthey were little things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:36.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他从不运动.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:40.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,从不洗自己的车\N甚至连一套运动服也没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never washes his car\Nand he doesn't even own a sports coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:43.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 你有没有做些什么\N去改善他?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, did you do\Nsomething about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.96,0:23:48.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 在我看完电视后,\N我决定要给自己一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.24,0:23:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, after l watched this TV show,\Nl decided l needed some me time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:50.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那段时间里\N我们不再见面.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during which\Nwe didn't see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:54.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正在那时\N我遇到了基巴·翠梅恩.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.01,0:23:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During which period\Nl met Dick Tremayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.39,0:24:00.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,荷恩百货店,\N男装部的.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.68,0:24:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horne's Department Store,\NMen's Fashions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:05.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他有好多大衣,而且他自己和车都\N总是保持得干净有型.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.25,0:24:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had lots of coats and keeps himself\Nand his car in great shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.16,0:24:13.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他的举止像只蠢驴,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.43,0:24:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of his behavior was asinine,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.79,0:24:16.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但总算和别人不一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.07,0:24:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but at least he was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.83,0:24:19.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在还有和这个基巴来往吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still seeing this Dick?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.21,0:24:25.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有了.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.51,0:24:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.55,0:24:29.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,露西, 你想和安迪\N和好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.81,0:24:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, do you wanna get\Nback together with Andy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.97,0:24:36.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.25,0:24:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.77,0:24:39.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 露西, 你能准确告诉我\N你到底想要什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.06,0:24:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Lucy, can you tell me exactly\Nwhat you do want?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.06,0:24:44.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.33,0:24:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.11,0:24:51.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法, 哈里, 真想帮帮她.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.40,0:24:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Harry, l was trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.91,0:24:53.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 有心就好.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.17,0:24:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was a good thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.95,0:24:58.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但有些事就像\N9号高速上的那个大坑一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.24,0:24:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's like trying to fix\Nthose potholes over on Highway 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.62,0:25:00.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一场大雨过后就...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.91,0:25:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First heavy rain and...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.63,0:25:03.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你开过那条路?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.91,0:25:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been down this road before?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.34,0:25:06.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当然开过.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.62,0:25:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure have.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.38,0:25:09.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.65,0:25:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.05,0:25:14.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在的情况很危险.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.32,0:25:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've got a dangerous situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.01,0:25:17.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经仔细考量过每一种可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.29,0:25:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've examined every possible angle
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.35,0:25:20.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信\N现在只有一条路能行得通.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.63,0:25:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l believe\Nthere's only one way to proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.60,0:25:23.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我个忙, 但只能你知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.87,0:25:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need a favor, strictly between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.73,0:25:25.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.00,0:25:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.94,0:25:29.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要一个书屋会的人.\N最棒的那个.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.21,0:25:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need one of the Bookhouse Boys.\NYour best man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.82,0:25:33.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话\N先别问我为什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.11,0:25:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt would be better\Nif you didn't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.58,0:25:37.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀, 只要你开口\N我会照办的.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.85,0:25:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooper, l've steered clear\Nwhen you asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.25,0:25:40.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么需要\N交待我的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.52,0:25:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls there anything l need to know\Nabout this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.83,0:25:42.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.12,0:25:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.63,0:25:45.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会安排的.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.89,0:25:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll set it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.34,0:25:47.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,9点半在公路旅社见.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.62,0:25:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine-thirty at the Roadhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.80,0:25:49.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.09,0:25:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.12,0:26:20.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 肯定是他.\N- 来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.39,0:26:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- lt must be him.\N- Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.54,0:26:25.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好, 先生,\N欢迎光临双食店.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.83,0:26:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, sir,\Nwelcome to the Double R Diner.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.42,0:26:27.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢, 可以要卡座吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.70,0:26:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, could l have a booth?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.25,0:26:29.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题, 这边请.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.53,0:26:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.01,0:26:39.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我们有2款\N特别美食精选--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.28,0:26:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have two very delicious\Nspecials this evening--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.77,0:26:43.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,给我来份\N半熟芝士汉堡,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.05,0:26:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sure you do but l'll have\Na cheeseburger, medium,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.64,0:26:46.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可乐和薯条.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.92,0:26:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Coke and some fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.27,0:26:48.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.55,0:26:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.24,0:26:53.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思, 陶德?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.52,0:26:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Toad?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.74,0:26:56.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不如我们到厨房\N那边去吃吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.03,0:26:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we finish this up\Nin the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.10,0:26:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.33,0:27:00.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,吃完收拾好\N别乱碰东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.60,0:27:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the back\Nand don't touch anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.25,0:27:02.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他只点了芝士汉堡.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.53,0:27:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He only wanted a cheeseburger.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.83,0:27:04.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定是美食评论家\N的个人癖好.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.10,0:27:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt must be some kind of\Nfood-critic trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.08,0:27:08.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你觉得是吗?\N- 绝对是, 呀. 我想--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.37,0:27:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You think so?\N- Absolutely, yeah. l think--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.84,0:27:16.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,洗手间?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.11,0:27:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.01,0:27:18.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 这边请, 先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.28,0:27:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right this way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.64,0:27:22.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚刚装修完\N感觉很好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.92,0:27:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just finished painting it\Nand it looks really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.35,0:27:24.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,独立单格都有门的的.\N是, 跟我来.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.62,0:27:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's completely private.\NYeah, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.64,0:27:26.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 对不起.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.92,0:27:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.31,0:27:28.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好东西.\N- 陶德!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.59,0:27:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good stuff.\N- Toad!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.11,0:27:32.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,陶德, 快给我出来...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.39,0:27:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toad, get out of my...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.30,0:27:56.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你能来见我.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.59,0:27:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.60,0:28:01.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不知道...\N- 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.86,0:28:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l didn't know...\N- Know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.02,0:28:04.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你受了什么刺激.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.29,0:28:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't know if you were mad or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.81,0:28:07.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说, 也许真刺激了你.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.10,0:28:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, how mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.81,0:28:09.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我受得了.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.10,0:28:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.98,0:28:14.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 我和詹姆斯之间\N真的没有什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.27,0:28:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, there's nothing going on\Nbetween me and James.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.45,0:28:15.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有又怎样呢? 我是说,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.74,0:28:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if there is? l mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.74,0:28:18.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谁规定我或詹姆斯\N不能和别人约会了?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.01,0:28:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who said James and l\Ncouldn't see other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.16,0:28:20.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定不会.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.44,0:28:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l certainly didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.49,0:28:25.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你意思是你也在\N和别人约会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.78,0:28:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you're seeing\Nsomeone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.63,0:28:31.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,马蒂, 我需要你帮忙.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.89,0:28:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maddy, l need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.01,0:28:38.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么帮?\N- 哈罗德·史密斯有劳拉的日记.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.29,0:28:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How?\N- Harold Smith has Laura's diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.18,0:28:41.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,警察不是已经\N有劳拉的日记了吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.46,0:28:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought the sheriff\Nhad Laura's diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.14,0:28:46.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗德说劳拉还有第二本日记\N我们不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.40,0:28:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harold said that Laura kept\Na second diary that l didn't know about
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.48,0:28:47.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在他那儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.77,0:28:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.19,0:28:49.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.47,0:28:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.82,0:28:53.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要告诉詹姆斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.08,0:28:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to tell James about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.03,0:28:58.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果劳拉真还有秘密日记...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.31,0:28:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf Laura did have a secret diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.20,0:29:01.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...而且在哈罗德那儿...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.48,0:29:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Harold's got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.07,0:29:05.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...我一定要拿到它\N你到底帮不帮我.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.35,0:29:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l'm gonna get it\Nwith or without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.96,0:29:10.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉詹姆斯去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.23,0:29:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell that to James.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.16,0:29:47.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我花太多钱买它了,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.43,0:29:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know l paid too much for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.41,0:29:50.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我真爱死它了.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.70,0:29:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but l just fell in love with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.04,0:29:53.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道那个售货员怎么说吗,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.34,0:29:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard the salesperson say,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.88,0:29:55.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"我们还在经营\N的唯一原因就是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.14,0:29:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''The only reason\Nwe're still in business
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.13,0:29:59.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为乔西·帕卡德\N来这里购物."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.41,0:29:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is because Josie Packard\Nbuys retail.''
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.47,0:30:03.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.75,0:30:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.14,0:30:06.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的吗?\N- 我喜欢, 真的.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.42,0:30:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You do?\N- l like it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.69,0:30:12.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你摸起来好冷.\N- 乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.96,0:30:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're so cold.\N- Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.81,0:30:15.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西, 我想知道.\N你真的去了西雅图吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.09,0:30:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie, l gotta know.\NWere you really in Seattle?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.73,0:30:19.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊, 你什么时候变的那么多疑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.99,0:30:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, why are you so suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.57,0:30:21.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看这些礼盒.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.87,0:30:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at these boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.11,0:30:24.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我是\N在这里买的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.40,0:30:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think l got them\Nat Cash and Carry?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.49,0:30:26.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么不告诉我一声\N就走了?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.77,0:30:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me\Nyou were going?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.74,0:30:29.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我必须避开,\N我好怕.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.01,0:30:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know l had to get away,\Nl was afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.50,0:30:32.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我明白, 你怕本和凯瑟琳.\N- 你知道的.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.77,0:30:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l know, afraid of Ben and Catherine.\N- You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.83,0:30:35.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是凯瑟琳现在已经死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.11,0:30:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now Catherine's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.55,0:30:38.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.82,0:30:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.84,0:30:41.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不会以为是我--\N- 我也不知道自己在想什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.12,0:30:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You don't think l--\N- l don't know what to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.05,0:30:45.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我真不知道.\N- 你以为是我烧了锯木厂?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.32,0:30:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l don't know.\N- You think l could burn the mill?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.26,0:30:48.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会亲手毁了\N自己的东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.52,0:30:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That l would ruin\Neverything of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.60,0:30:50.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,保险金啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.89,0:30:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's insurance money.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.31,0:30:54.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.60,0:30:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.86,0:30:57.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.13,0:30:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.40,0:31:02.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然把我想的\N那么恶毒?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.67,0:31:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you think\Nof such terrible things?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.03,0:31:05.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然这样来伤我的心?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.31,0:31:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you hurt me so?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.38,0:31:22.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过太焦虑了.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.66,0:31:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was just so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.22,0:31:27.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很对不起.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.50,0:31:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.56,0:31:29.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,抱着我.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.83,0:31:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.64,0:31:31.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,抱着我.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.94,0:31:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.10,0:31:35.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 要我.\N- 乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.37,0:31:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Take me.\N- Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.27,0:31:37.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我好想你要我.\N- 乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.54,0:31:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l want you to take me.\N- Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.73,0:31:41.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西, 为什么?\N为什么你告诉我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.01,0:31:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie, why?\NWhy didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.08,0:31:51.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,撕开它.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.36,0:31:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.41,0:31:53.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.69,0:31:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.04,0:31:55.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,撕开它.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.33,0:31:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.89,0:32:11.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想要你.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.17,0:32:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.27,0:32:15.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.55,0:32:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.11,0:32:25.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.39,0:32:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.40,0:32:27.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,胜过我自己的生命.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.69,0:32:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,more than my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.73,0:33:04.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨, 美媚.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.03,0:33:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, good-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.44,0:33:07.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不给我来杯好咖啡\N慰劳一下嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.73,0:33:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you have to grease\Nto get some coffee around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.03,0:33:11.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,斯登伍法官.\N你好, 法官大人.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.30,0:33:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judge Sternwood.\NHello, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.49,0:33:14.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,露西, 你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.77,0:33:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, you're a cool drink of water
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.83,0:33:17.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,两眼泪汪汪的.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.11,0:33:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to road-weary eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.25,0:33:18.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,藏着什么秘密呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.54,0:33:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.96,0:33:23.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还是别提了它, 先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.25,0:33:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'd rather not talk about it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.30,0:33:26.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们来抱抱吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.58,0:33:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.22,0:33:34.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,生活艰难啊, 亲爱的.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.49,0:33:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is hard, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.56,0:33:37.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此, 还是要...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.83,0:33:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still and all, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.19,0:33:40.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道还有很多地方\N比双峰镇过的艰难多了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.46,0:33:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's harder in most places\Nthan in Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.90,0:33:42.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,克林顿.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.17,0:33:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clinton.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.07,0:33:44.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,我来晚了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.34,0:33:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry l'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.57,0:33:47.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 我也是刚到.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.84,0:33:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l only just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.20,0:33:49.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,见到你真好.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.47,0:33:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.24,0:33:53.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫什么, 哈里?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.51,0:33:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's her name, Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.25,0:33:56.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 啊?\N- 你好像刚刚驯完
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.51,0:33:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?\N- You got the look of a man
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.21,0:33:58.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一匹小母马, 我的儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.48,0:33:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with filly trouble, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.17,0:34:03.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果它们不愿意上鞍,\N那你有2个选择.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.45,0:34:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf they don't take the saddle,\Nyou got two options.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.09,0:34:06.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 一定有一个能奏效.\N- 哈里?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.36,0:34:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- And l won't bore you with either one.\N- Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.92,0:34:10.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,斯登伍法官,\N特别探员戴尔·库珀.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.19,0:34:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judge Sternwood,\NSpecial Agent Dale Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.59,0:34:11.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,联邦调查局.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.86,0:34:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FBl.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.18,0:34:15.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好么,小伙子?\N- 你好,法官大人.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.46,0:34:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How are you, lad?\N- Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.72,0:34:17.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们2个\N有很多共同点.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.00,0:34:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two should have\Na lot in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.27,0:34:19.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,希很快就会把法庭日程表带来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.54,0:34:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid will bring in the court calendar
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.10,0:34:22.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,像醉倒北印第安人\N那么快.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.37,0:34:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as soon as the Winnebago\Nis tanked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.86,0:34:25.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你想看你在爱尔兰帮我\N收藏的那封密信吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.14,0:34:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna break the seal\Non that lrish you stashed for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.40,0:34:27.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这边谈.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.68,0:34:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.95,0:34:33.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀先生, 你是怎么找到\N我们这个小地方的?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.21,0:34:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Cooper, how do you find\Nour little corner of this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.41,0:34:35.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这里美的像天堂, 先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.69,0:34:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.49,0:34:38.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 这周, 天堂发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.75,0:34:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this week, heaven includes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.62,0:34:42.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,纵火案, 多起谋杀案
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.89,0:34:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,arson, multiple homicides
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.67,0:34:45.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还差点要了\N联邦探员的名.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.93,0:34:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and an attempt on the life\Nof a federal agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.05,0:34:49.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,天堂是个总是给人\N意外的大地方, 先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.33,0:34:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven is a large\Nand interesting place, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.43,0:34:55.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,露西?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.71,0:34:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.02,0:34:58.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,基巴.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.28,0:34:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.68,0:35:00.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,露西, 我寝不宁.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.94,0:35:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, l haven't slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.85,0:35:02.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,食不安.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.15,0:35:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.61,0:35:06.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一直沉浸在巨大的痛苦之中.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.88,0:35:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been absolutely miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.90,0:35:09.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你有么?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.19,0:35:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.07,0:35:13.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得自己卑鄙,无耻,下流,愚蠢至极,\N我所做的让我觉得...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.36,0:35:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been a fool, a cad,\Nthe way l've behaved and l'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.70,0:35:16.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,极其, 极其羞耻.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.96,0:35:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm deeply, deeply ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.58,0:35:20.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.86,0:35:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.33,0:35:22.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经在脑海里反覆\N挣扎过百万次了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.60,0:35:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been over it in my mind\Na million times
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.29,0:35:24.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我终于来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.57,0:35:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and what l've come to is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.42,0:35:27.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.70,0:35:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have to--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.21,0:35:30.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 我必须要做出正确的事了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.47,0:35:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, l must do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.30,0:35:34.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.58,0:35:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.56,0:35:37.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.82,0:35:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.85,0:35:40.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我决定把一切都\N结束了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.12,0:35:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's everything l could\Nscrape together.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.39,0:35:42.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的筋疲力尽了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.69,0:35:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm completely knackered.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.61,0:35:51.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.89,0:35:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.03,0:35:55.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,6百50美元.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.30,0:35:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six hundred and fifty dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.37,0:35:56.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我打电话咨询过了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.63,0:35:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've called around.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.91,0:35:59.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这些钱\N足够有余了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.20,0:35:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been told\Nit's more than adequate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.58,0:36:03.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么有余?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.84,0:36:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.25,0:36:05.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,做那个--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.51,0:36:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.17,0:36:07.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是处理那个--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.44,0:36:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To take care of--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.75,0:36:10.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白的...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.01,0:36:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.46,0:36:12.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...那个小麻烦.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.75,0:36:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the little problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.88,0:36:15.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,理查,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.15,0:36:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.01,0:36:18.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你接下来要做的:
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.29,0:36:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,here's what you're going to do:
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.14,0:36:21.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好你的钱,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.42,0:36:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your money,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.56,0:36:25.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,放回你的钱包\N或口袋里,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.83,0:36:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,put it back in your wallet\Nor your pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.69,0:36:28.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,转身起步走, 然后\N穿过这两道门--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.96,0:36:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,turn around and walk through\Nboth sets of doors--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.94,0:36:31.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,第二道有时会有点卡.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.23,0:36:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second one sticks sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.24,0:36:35.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,--出门直接到停车场,\N上车, 启动,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.50,0:36:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--go out into the parking lot,\Nget in your car, turn the key,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.20,0:36:39.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后, 只要你还活着一天
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.47,0:36:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and never, ever speak to me again
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.04,0:36:42.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就再也不要来和我说话了!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.31,0:36:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.54,0:36:46.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你敢再多说一个字我就尖叫.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.81,0:36:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say one more word and l'll scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.46,0:36:47.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,滚, 请滚吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.75,0:36:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.69,0:37:05.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,基巴!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.97,0:37:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.27,0:37:11.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,基巴.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.54,0:37:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.37,0:37:22.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.65,0:37:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.16,0:37:26.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...我深感遗憾.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.42,0:37:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is most difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.83,0:37:28.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对你痛失亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.09,0:37:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest condolences
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.42,0:37:32.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我表示最深切的慰问.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.69,0:37:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on your heartbreaking loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.42,0:37:35.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.70,0:37:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.13,0:37:40.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在法庭见过你\N很多次了.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.40,0:37:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've appeared before me\Nmany times.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.31,0:37:44.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是一个很好的,\N大方得体的人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.57,0:37:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know you to be a fine,\Ndecent man
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.52,0:37:46.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是个很有才干的律师.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.81,0:37:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a capable attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.06,0:37:50.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看到这种事\N发生在你身上...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.35,0:37:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to see you under\Nthese circumstances is...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.94,0:37:53.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都很震惊.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.22,0:37:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls dreadful for us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.86,0:37:56.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,既然, 法律提供了一个架构
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.12,0:37:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the law provides a structure
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.49,0:37:59.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,指导并引领我们渡过\N艰难险阻的时刻.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.75,0:38:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to guide us through\Nperilous and trying times.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.62,0:38:06.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,同时它也要求我们以更坚强的意志\N去服从它, 秉公执法.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.89,0:38:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it requires our submission\Nto its procedures and higher purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.08,0:38:12.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当我们下定决心要在这场永恒的人间戏剧\N里承担各自不同的角色...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.37,0:38:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we assume our respective roles\Nin this enduring drama...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.01,0:38:16.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...我这样说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.27,0:38:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just let me say that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.80,0:38:21.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须鼓起勇气去面对\N栖息在我们意志中
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.08,0:38:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when these frail shadows\Nwe inhabit now
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.14,0:38:24.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,最薄弱的阴暗面,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.41,0:38:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have quit the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.68,0:38:27.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我们会再次相聚在
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.95,0:38:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll meet
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.14,0:38:31.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,死神的瓦尔哈拉神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.42,0:38:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and raise a glass again together
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.07,0:38:34.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,并举杯痛饮.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.36,0:38:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in Valhalla.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.20,0:38:41.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信会的.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.46,0:38:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would that it were so.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.87,0:38:46.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对你提出自辩的请求\N我表示理解.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.13,0:38:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l understand it's your intention\Nto represent yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.33,0:38:49.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.61,0:38:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.29,0:38:53.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 洛威呢,\N那个检察官?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.58,0:38:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, where's Lodwick,\Nthe prosecutor?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.13,0:38:55.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 还没到呢.\N- 这样吧, 我看
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.41,0:38:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Overdue.\N- Well, l suggest
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.13,0:38:58.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们明早再决定\N保释的事吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.41,0:38:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we leave the question of bail\Ntill morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.30,0:39:02.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你对此决定满意吗, 利兰?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.58,0:39:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The facilities are adequate, Leland?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.55,0:39:03.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 满意.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.82,0:39:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.06,0:39:07.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人对我都非常仁慈.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.32,0:39:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has been most kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.48,0:39:09.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就晚安吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.76,0:39:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll say good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.52,0:39:11.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 副警长.\N- 晚安.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.79,0:39:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Deputy.\N- Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.03,0:39:16.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.30,0:39:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.79,0:39:27.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里说吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.04,0:39:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll speak for us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.54,0:39:31.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这事非常棘手.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.81,0:39:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have hard jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.34,0:39:38.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,出庭名单定了.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.62,0:39:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready to roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.80,0:39:43.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦, 嗨, 希.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.06,0:39:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hi, Sid.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.10,0:39:45.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.36,0:39:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.39,0:39:48.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,希, 快向特派探员\N库珀问好.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.66,0:39:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid, say hello\Nto Special Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.43,0:39:51.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 库珀探员,你好.\N- 你好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.70,0:39:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Agent Cooper.\N- How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.35,0:39:53.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 先生们,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.64,0:39:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.90,0:39:57.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经赶了\N8小时的路.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.17,0:39:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've been eight hours\Non the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.65,0:40:01.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,希和我准备挤进\N大北方酒店,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.94,0:40:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid and l are gonna pile it over\Nto The Great Northern,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.74,0:40:05.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,找上小维尼一起\N去大木房里用个美餐.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.01,0:40:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hook up the Winne\Nand dine in the Timber Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.70,0:40:08.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,法庭上见.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.98,0:40:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.00,0:40:15.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他妻子?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.26,0:40:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.21,0:40:19.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,法律秘书.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.50,0:40:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law clerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.09,0:40:22.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好家伙啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.36,0:40:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.64,0:40:28.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 今晚的事都安排好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.90,0:40:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, is everything set for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.72,0:40:30.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,都安排妥了.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.01,0:40:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.81,0:40:32.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.08,0:40:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.07,0:40:42.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你朋友卡特里娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.35,0:40:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls this your friend Katrina?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.65,0:40:45.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特里娜? 卡特里娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.92,0:40:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katrina? Katrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.45,0:40:49.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这位小姐叫...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.72,0:40:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.08,0:40:54.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这边来, 小姐们.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.36,0:40:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come along, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.17,0:41:37.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 托吉麻辣先生. 我们都安排好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.44,0:41:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Mr. Tojamura. We're all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.92,0:41:40.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请问, 你使用什么\N信用卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.18,0:41:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what credit card\Ndo you wanna put that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.42,0:41:43.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麻烦你, 我付现金.\N- 现金?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.68,0:41:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Cash, please.\N- Cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.63,0:41:45.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.92,0:41:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.64,0:41:48.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚说\N你从哪里来, 先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.92,0:41:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you say\Nyou traveled from, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.68,0:41:51.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 西雅图.\N- 西雅图?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.95,0:41:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Seattle.\N- Seattle?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.81,0:41:55.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 那, 其实也不是很远.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.09,0:41:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not such a long trip, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.02,0:41:58.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊, 托吉麻辣先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.29,0:41:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good, Mr. Tojamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.44,0:42:00.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,行李生会把行李直接\N送到你房间的.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.70,0:42:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bellman will take you\Nup to your suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.03,0:42:02.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.30,0:42:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you would like to treat yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.78,0:42:06.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,品尝到最地道的\N风味菜,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.07,0:42:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to some of our outstanding\Nlocal cuisine while you're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.24,0:42:09.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我推介你去\N双食店.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.50,0:42:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l would recommend\Nthe Double R Diner.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.16,0:42:12.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,找诺玛就行了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.44,0:42:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask for Norma.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.25,0:42:14.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.51,0:42:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.80,0:42:25.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,诺玛, 我是路易.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.09,0:42:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Norma, it's Louie.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.30,0:42:28.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,目标人物出现了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.59,0:42:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think the eagle has landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.01,0:42:34.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 皮特, 见见我表弟乔纳森.\N- 乔纳森.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.30,0:42:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Pete, meet my cousin Jonathan.\N- Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.10,0:42:38.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为表弟叫"乔"吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.37,0:42:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thinking cousin have some joe?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.31,0:42:41.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,飞了那么长时间\N人物锺都乱了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.60,0:42:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a long flight it will help him\Nreset his biographical clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.94,0:42:45.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是 "生物钟."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.21,0:42:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ''biological.''
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.82,0:42:47.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是,我刚好沏了茶.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.11,0:42:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think so, l just made a fresh pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.03,0:42:50.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来. 马上给乔泡一杯.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.31,0:42:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Cup of joe coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.74,0:42:53.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 生物钟.\N- 生物钟.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.02,0:42:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Biological.\N- Biological.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.75,0:42:58.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道你这6年怎么过的.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.02,0:42:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know how you lasted six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.13,0:43:01.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,除了乡巴佬和\N民工,就没别的了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.39,0:43:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing but hayseeds\Nand manual laborers.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.38,0:43:03.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,耶, 我们的任务不同嘛.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.66,0:43:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we all got our job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.63,0:43:05.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的差不多完成了吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.90,0:43:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours is nearly finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.80,0:43:08.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,锯木厂和帕卡德的地\N都卖出了?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.06,0:43:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sale of the mill\Nand the Packard lands?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.01,0:43:11.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,合同一签就成了.\N我要等皮特签名.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.27,0:43:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signing the contracts soon.\Nl need Pete's signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.80,0:43:14.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他的凯瑟琳的继承人.\N- 会很麻烦吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.07,0:43:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He's Catherine's heir.\N- Will that be difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.31,0:43:16.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不会.\N- 要多久?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.57,0:43:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- No.\N- How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.48,0:43:19.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 2天.\N- 我们计划回香港了.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.74,0:43:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Two days.\N- We're expected back in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.02,0:43:23.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,埃卡先生急着\N想见你.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.28,0:43:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Eckhardt wants very much\Nto see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.78,0:43:27.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么其它变化吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.05,0:43:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other complications?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.91,0:43:30.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,汉克那边可能有点难搞.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.19,0:43:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a problem with Hank.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.95,0:43:33.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.22,0:43:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.91,0:43:37.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有人会怀疑我们吗?\N- 肯定不会.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.19,0:43:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are we suspected?\N- Certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.83,0:43:39.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个警长呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.10,0:43:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about this sheriff?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.08,0:43:41.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我对他没意思.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.36,0:43:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.67,0:43:43.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是问你这个.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.93,0:43:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what l asked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.97,0:43:57.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,9点半, 不迟不早刚刚好.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.25,0:43:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine-thirty, right on the tick.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.48,0:44:00.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.75,0:44:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.27,0:44:02.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,到了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.55,0:44:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.41,0:44:13.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有什么急事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.70,0:44:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we in any particular hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.83,0:44:15.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.10,0:44:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.49,0:44:18.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我请你喝杯啤酒. 酒保?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.77,0:44:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let me buy you a beer. Bartender?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.71,0:44:23.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别敲了, 就来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.97,0:44:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, l'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.00,0:44:25.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别敲了!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.28,0:44:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.96,0:44:30.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 我们还没开--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.25,0:44:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're not op--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.97,0:44:37.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哼, 放屁.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.25,0:44:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fart.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.16,0:44:54.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有啥事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.44,0:44:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.62,0:45:05.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我认识你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.88,0:45:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do l know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.80,0:45:14.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.06,0:45:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.87,0:45:40.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,听着, 我想就这样\N躺一会算了.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.15,0:45:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, l think l'm just gonna\Nlay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.46,0:45:42.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.72,0:45:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.96,0:45:44.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,到底咋回事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.22,0:45:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.05,0:45:59.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,滴血为盟,\N下次我会把你头拧下来.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.33,0:45:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood brother,\Nnext time l take your head off.
